Key Match Events: Evidence Magkopa scores the opening goal for South Africa on 57 minutes
Hakimi misses a penalty for Morocco on 85 minutes
Teboho Mokoena scores a second goal for South Africa from a freekick in the 90+5th minute
Amrabat receives a straight red card for Morocco in the 90+2nd minute
Post-Match Reflections: South Africa's win marks a significant upset as Morocco were tournament favorites
Morocco's elimination from the tournament comes after a strong group stage performance where they topped their group with seven points
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in the San-Pedro stadium
South Africa will face Cape Verde in the quarter-finals, while Morocco's time in the tournament has come to an end
Others: The match was a Last 16 match of the Africa Cup of Nations 2023
Both teams sang their national anthems before the match and shook hands
